1
00:00:31,875 --> 00:00:35,285
[CHATTERING]

2
00:00:45,458 --> 00:00:47,458
[LIGHTSABER HUMMING]

3
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,330
You're right on time.

4
00:00:56,416 --> 00:00:58,576
Oh, really? I thought I was late.

5
00:00:58,666 --> 00:00:59,706
That's what I meant.

6
00:01:03,291 --> 00:01:04,831
She's a fast learner.

7
00:01:05,666 --> 00:01:06,996
I really wouldn't know.

8
00:01:10,208 --> 00:01:11,288
[SYSTEM CHIMES]

9
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:14,710
[LIGHTSABER RETRACTS]

10
00:01:22,041 --> 00:01:24,581
[WHIRRING, CLICKING]

11
00:01:24,666 --> 00:01:28,666
These are the new training remotes
designed to simulate battle droids.

12
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,290
[DROID SHRIEKS]

13
00:01:53,875 --> 00:01:55,285
[DROID SPUTTERS]

14
00:02:07,708 --> 00:02:08,998
[SYSTEM CHIMES]

15
00:02:11,166 --> 00:02:12,206
Impressive.

16
00:02:13,041 --> 00:02:14,251
[SIGHS]

17
00:02:16,041 --> 00:02:20,041
[COMMS CHATTER]

18
00:02:21,625 --> 00:02:23,495
Thanks for coming, Master.

19
00:02:23,583 --> 00:02:25,293
Well, I was in the area.

20
00:02:26,166 --> 00:02:27,376
Any thoughts?

21
00:02:29,875 --> 00:02:30,955
You don't wanna know.

22
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,500
What's the problem?

23
00:02:47,583 --> 00:02:48,883
[JEDI MURMURING]

24
00:02:58,333 --> 00:03:00,633
[SCOFFS] It's a lousy test.

25
00:03:00,708 --> 00:03:02,918
But it's what every Jedi does.

26
00:03:03,416 --> 00:03:04,496
Exactly.

27
00:03:06,916 --> 00:03:08,376
Look, you want a real test?

28
00:03:08,458 --> 00:03:09,458
Name it.

29
00:03:09,541 --> 00:03:11,831
Okay, I'll make you an actual test,

30
00:03:11,916 --> 00:03:13,666
and then we'll see
what you've really learned.

31
00:03:31,041 --> 00:03:34,041
[GUNSHIP APPROACHING]

32
00:03:47,958 --> 00:03:48,958
You're right on time.

33
00:03:49,041 --> 00:03:50,381
I thought I was late.

34
00:03:50,458 --> 00:03:51,578
That's what I mean.

35
00:04:03,916 --> 00:04:06,706
Captain Rex and the boys have agreed
to help with the test.

36
00:04:06,791 --> 00:04:08,251
It's our privilege, Commander.

37
00:04:08,333 --> 00:04:10,753
Let's get started. Head out to the center.

38
00:04:13,083 --> 00:04:14,923
Make sure your blasters are set to stun.

39
00:04:15,583 --> 00:04:19,173
Droids are predictable.
I want you to be prepared for anything.

40
00:04:25,708 --> 00:04:27,958
You need to remain calm. Think.

41
00:04:28,041 --> 00:04:31,081
Feel the intention
of the trooper who will fire first.

42
00:04:31,166 --> 00:04:34,376
You should be able to sense the moment
before they even pull the trigger.

43
00:04:35,833 --> 00:04:37,003
You ready?

44
00:04:50,208 --> 00:04:51,328
Begin.

45
00:05:00,291 --> 00:05:01,791
[GRUNTS]

46
00:05:01,875 --> 00:05:03,245
[THUDS]

47
00:05:06,791 --> 00:05:09,041
[VOICE ECHOING]
Don't worry, Rex. She'll wake up.

48
00:05:09,916 --> 00:05:12,456
[NORMAL] That's it. Come on.
You'll get used to it. Wake up.

49
00:05:14,958 --> 00:05:16,458
[GROANS]

50
00:05:16,541 --> 00:05:18,791
[SIGHS] How long was I out?

51
00:05:18,875 --> 00:05:20,705
- An hour.
- An hour?

52
00:05:20,791 --> 00:05:23,711
Yeah, Jesse really tagged you.

53
00:05:23,791 --> 00:05:25,421
Sorry, Commander.

54
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:26,710
Come on. Let's go again.

55
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:36,500
You ready?

56
00:05:41,333 --> 00:05:42,333
Begin.

57
00:05:52,541 --> 00:05:54,081
- [GROANS]
- [ANAKIN] Let's go again.

58
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:07,750
Again.

59
00:06:13,291 --> 00:06:14,501
Again.

60
00:06:14,583 --> 00:06:15,423
Again.

61
00:06:16,833 --> 00:06:18,883
- [GROANS]
- [ANAKIN] Again.

62
00:06:20,291 --> 00:06:21,331
Again.

63
00:06:34,458 --> 00:06:36,878
I don't know how much more of this
she can take.

64
00:06:36,958 --> 00:06:38,958
Eh. She'll be fine.

65
00:06:44,375 --> 00:06:46,125
Well, you're waking up faster.

66
00:06:46,208 --> 00:06:47,498
[GROANS]

67
00:06:47,583 --> 00:06:49,383
This is ridiculous.

68
00:06:49,458 --> 00:06:52,538
The droids aren't half as good
as Rex's men.

69
00:06:52,625 --> 00:06:53,665
That's the point.

70
00:06:55,458 --> 00:06:59,208
Look, I know this is tough,
but... [SIGHS] ...I want it to be difficult.

71
00:06:59,291 --> 00:07:02,461
This is about life and death.

72
00:07:02,541 --> 00:07:05,501
And as your master,
I'm responsible for you.

73
00:07:05,583 --> 00:07:10,003
The best way I can protect you is
to teach you how to protect yourself.

74
00:07:11,666 --> 00:07:13,536
And if you can hold off Rex and the boys,

75
00:07:13,625 --> 00:07:15,625
you'll be ready for anything
on a battlefield.

76
00:07:16,125 --> 00:07:18,825
Well, eh,
anything with a blaster at least.

77
00:07:23,166 --> 00:07:24,416
You ready?

78
00:07:27,916 --> 00:07:30,536
All right, boys, let's go again.

79
00:07:58,416 --> 00:07:59,786
- [BLASTER FIRES]
- [AHSOKA GRUNTS]

80
00:08:06,541 --> 00:08:07,541
[COMMS CHATTER]

81
00:08:07,625 --> 00:08:11,205
Not bad. It took us five minutes
to knock you out that time.

82
00:08:13,291 --> 00:08:14,291
I can do better.

83
00:08:20,625 --> 00:08:21,745
Begin.

84
00:08:44,833 --> 00:08:45,883
[BLAST IMPACTS]

85
00:08:50,708 --> 00:08:53,708
[RUMBLING]

86
00:08:53,791 --> 00:08:57,291
[ALARM BLARING]

87
00:09:12,166 --> 00:09:14,496
Let's hope all that training pays off.

88
00:09:25,791 --> 00:09:26,961
[REX] Hold your fire!

89
00:09:28,375 --> 00:09:30,205
[JESSE] Hang on.
We have Tano and the commander.

90
00:09:30,291 --> 00:09:32,171
Send all remaining troops to my position.

